entries.journal_entry_description: Retrieve containers of poached goods from the Chiss poacher camp.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Sordaan has asked you to help out the chief of his security force, Manfred Carter.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Manfred wants you to retrieve 12 containers of poached goods from the Chiss poacher camp on the far west side of the region.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Deliver the poached goods you recovered from the Chiss poachers to Kerssoc. Kerssoc is in the small Rodian camp outside of the Etyyy gate.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Deliver the recovered goods to Kerssoc
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Manfred Carter at the main Rodian hunting camp in Etyyy, the Hunting Grounds..
